OL,5,G2305 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,6,     FDoreen and Franky masquerade as
OL,7,     Fnuns to con people. Greg hires
OL,8,     FSteve Wilson as Karen's new
OL,9,     Flawyer. New prisoner Monica turns
OL,10,     Fout to be an old friends with Bea
OL,11,     Fand Lizzie.
OL,12,G0005 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,13,     FMonica agrees to Bea's suggestion
OL,14,     Fthat she let Marilyn and Eddie run
OL,15,     Fher milkbar while she is inside.
OL,16,     FMarilyn is released. Meg and Karen
OL,17,     Ffind Lynn on the floor of her
OL,18,     Fcell, bleeding.
